ActCriminal Code
SubjectOrder Amending the Order Designating Manitoba for the Purposes of the Criminal Interest Rate Provisions of the Criminal Code
PrecisOrder amending the ORDER DESIGNATING MANITOBA FOR THE PURPOSES OF THE CRIMINAL INTEREST RATE PROVISIONS OF THE CRIMINAL CODE which modifies the coming into force section of the Designation Order so that it mirrors the new Manitoba legislative measures. The Order, as amended, will come into force when the named legislative measures come into force.
